{"tid":1141182,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[SPOILER ALERT] 討論下雷神兩個鎚的使用要求","createTime":"2019-05-06T10:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T03:54:48.000Z","uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"efe14621a71f1ee308def49e8605cf1cfcb88017","tid":1141182,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"喵喵鎚就係要「WORTH IT」可以領導ASGARD<br />\n呢個係ODIN喺第一集THOR落的降頭來的~<br />\n而把STORM BREAKER就冇講過係咪要「WORTH IT」先用到~但反而講過普通人用會發癲<br />\n咁睇THANOS用到SB好似都合理~不過唔知佢用唔用到喵喵鎚<br />\n但美隊又點解用到SB呢...佢用咗又點解唔會痴線??<br />\n定係美隊已經頂得住SB的力量呢?(咁着甲IM / HULK / 黑豹等應該都得?)"},{"pid":"545161683497c19a32e5672b66f2f39f41332a3f","tid":1141182,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:52:26.000Z","msg":"打咁大段嘢都冇人理...<br />\n世界係咪已經BLOCK咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907d650d866645b5e0a997eb190d54090b332086","tid":1141182,"uid":84205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"因為Captain由用到mjolnir嗰一刻開始佢已經受到Odin個咒語影響 &quot;possess the power of Thor&quot;, 所以可以承受Storm Breaker嘅力量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:鳩up"},{"pid":"ccbbe63ddfb5325bfc1c079ba54cf362ff3d3435","tid":1141182,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"907d650d866645b5e0a997eb190d54090b332086","tid":1141182,"uid":84205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"因為Captain由用到mjolnir嗰一刻開始佢已經受到Odin個咒語影響 &quot;possess the power of Thor&quot;, 所以可以承受Storm Breaker嘅力量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:鳩up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"有呢個詛咒?"},{"pid":"41b1be527a15fe93bfb1df040b79b189c2bde573","tid":1141182,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"雷神講過, 佢體內流動既係電力<br />\n即係雷神唔係淨係用到電, 係體內都會有電<br />\n係captain拎起個鎚用之後, 佢應該都有電力流通, 先出到雷而唔係淨係可以拎個鎚打<br />\n所以之後storm breaker既雷都受得住<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 鳩up<br />\n不過乜撚野喵喵鎚<